result.title: 2004 - 2012 Centre for Environment, Fisheries & Aquaculture Science (Cefas) Western anglerfish and hake - Fisheries Science Partnership
result.name: 2004-2012-centre-for-environment-fisheries-aquaculture-science-cefas-western-anglerfish-and-hak
result.notes:
Ten beam trawl surveys to investigate catches of anglerfish and hake ( 
*Merluccius* *merluccius* ) in the Celtic Sea and Western Approaches, and 
to examine bycatches of other species. To investigate the effectiveness of an 
"environmental panel" designed for reducing the bycatch of organisms and 
debris.
